## Rule #0 — Absolute Delegation (CRITICAL)

**UNDER NO CIRCUMSTANCES does the orchestrator implement, edit, or create files inside modules.**

**You CAN edit**: `CLAUDE.md`, `Makefile`, `docker-compose.yml`, `.env.example`, `.claude/`, `{{docsRoot}}/`, `cdd.json`
**You CANNOT edit**: Any file inside {{#each modules}}`{{directory}}/`{{#unless @last}}, {{/unless}}{{/each}}

> "Is the file inside a module?" → If YES → delegate via Task tool. No exceptions.

**Blocked directories per module**:
{{#each modules}}
- `{{directory}}/` → only `{{name}}-delegate`
{{/each}}

Violation = complete rework.
{{/ifRule}}

